      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg/330px-Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"226\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg/500px-Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg/960px-Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stefan Meyer-Kahlen <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist, professional computer chess programmer, and author of <a href=\"/Shredder\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. In the early 90s Stefan started chess programming and co-authored <a href=\"/XXXX\" title=\"XXXX\">XXXX</a> in cooperation with his fellow <a href=\"/Martin_Zentner\" title=\"Martin Zentner\">Martin Zentner</a>. He began to develop his own program Shredder in early 1995. After winning the <a href=\"/WMCCC_1996\" title=\"WMCCC 1996\">WMCCC 1996</a> in Djakarta, he started his professional career. Along with <a href=\"/SOS\" title=\"SOS\">SOS</a> author <a href=\"/Rudolf_Huber\" title=\"Rudolf Huber\">Rudolf Huber</a>, Stefan Meyer-Kahlen designed the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> protocol, released in 2000 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#SMK\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SMK</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Interviews\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Interviews</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.thorstenczub.de/Paderborn.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Stefanmeyerkahlen.jpg\" src=\"/images/8/8b/Stefanmeyerkahlen.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"754\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Theo_van_der_Storm\" title=\"Theo van der Storm\">Theo van der Storm</a> and SMK, celebrating <a href=\"/IPCCC_1998\" title=\"IPCCC 1998\">IPCCC 1998</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Meyer-Kahlen,Stefan_Fritz,Axel_2001.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Meyer-Kahlen,Stefan Fritz,Axel 2001.jpg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fe/Meyer-Kahlen%2CStefan_Fritz%2CAxel_2001.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div>\n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> talking with Axel Fritz about <a href=\"/Fritz#PocketFritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Pocket Fritz</a>, 2001 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, <a href=\"/Jens_Lieberum\" title=\"Jens Lieberum\">Jens Lieberum</a>, <a href=\"/Johan_de_Koning\" title=\"Johan de Koning\">Johan de Koning</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Rolle&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Thomas Rolle (page does not exist)\">Thomas Rolle</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=J%C3%B6rg_Sameith&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jörg Sameith (page does not exist)\">Jörg Sameith</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Five visualizations of the k-best mode.</i> <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=26448\">Autoplayer for Win32 (again)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 12, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=52542\">ELO performance?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 22, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a>, <a href=\"/Pawn_Advantage,_Win_Percentage,_and_Elo\" title=\"Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo\">Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=111002\">Definition of the Extended Autoplayer 232 Protocol</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Auto232\" title=\"Auto232\">Auto232</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=137052\">EPD format</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=141612\">UCI (=universal chess interface)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 28, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=360181\">Extension of the UCI protocol</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61895\">Deep Shredder 13 Windows out</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SMK\">SMK</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: SMK\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=63\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/authors.htm\">Meet the Authors</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.chessbase.com/portals/3/files/2004/ausflug/gruppemitnamen.jpg\">Who is Who at ChessBase</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.chessbase.com/home/TabId/176/PostId/303269\">ChessBase auf Helgoland</a> June 16, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.althofer.de/workshop-2008.html\">Workshop Jena 2008: Analysis, Design, and Programming of Games</a> pictorial report by <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Interviews\">Interviews</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Interviews\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/alte_daten/chesstigers_alt/ChessClassic2001/CompMatches/stefan_meyer_kahlen.htm\">Lokalverbot für Westentaschen-Großmeister</a> - Interview mit <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>, 2001 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schach-welt.de/schach/computerschach/interviews/stefan-meyer-kahlen-2006\">Interview with Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.chessbase.com/post/shredder-10-now-available\">Shredder 10 now available - Interview with Shredder author Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase News</a>, May 26, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.shredderchess.de/schach-news/shredder-news/interview-stefan-meyer%11kahlen.html\">Interview mit Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Diosi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Diosi (page does not exist)\">Michael Diosi</a>, October 2007 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://glareanverlag.wordpress.com/2009/06/30/interview-mit-dem-shredder-programmierer-stefan-meyer-kahlen/\">Interview mit dem Schach-Programmierer Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://glareanverlag.wordpress.com/\">Glarean Magazin</a>, June 30, 2009 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schach-welt.de/schach/computerschach/interviews/stefan-meyer-kahlen-2010\">Interview with Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, February 21, 2010 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://letscast.fm/sites/let-s-talk-about-chess-753d92ea/episode/12-stefan-meyer-kahlen-shredderchess\">#12 Stefan Meyer-Kahlen (ShredderChess) | Let's talk about chess</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Podcast\">Podcast</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>, December 02, 2020 <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Self-photographed, 2008, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.shredderchess.com/\">Shredder Computer Chess</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=141612\">UCI (=universal chess interface)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 28, 2000</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.thorstenczub.de/Paderborn.html\">Ein Besuch in Paderborn 1998</a> by <a href=\"/Thorsten_Czub\" title=\"Thorsten Czub\">Thorsten Czub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> interviewed by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.karlonline.org/302_4.htm\">Axel Fritz</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schach.com/\">Schach.com</a>), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chess_Classic\">Chess Classic Mainz 2001</a>, Photographer <a href=\"/Gerhard_Hund\" title=\"Gerhard Hund\">Gerhard Hund</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.althofer.de/k-best-visualisations.html\">K-Best Visualisations</a> by <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75968\">Let's talk about chess .